column2: b'Precure All Stars Movie DX: Minna Tomodachi\xe2\x98\x86Kiseki no Zenin Daishuugou!'

b'Love, Miki and Inori are on their way to a dance contest, but get lost on their way to Minato Mirai. Still looking for their way, they are attacked by a monster. When the three Fresh Precure girls start to fight it, other Precures show up to support them. They all have to combine their powers to win against this mighty enemy.'
